__SqlMetric__.verbose_name: % of records where zip code is consistent with county code

__SqlMetric__.expression:
(#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll) FILTER (
        WHERE consistent_dob = 'CONSISTENT'
        AND consistent_dod <> 'AMBIGUOUS'
        AND consistent_race = 'CONSISTENT'
        AND consistent_sex = 'CONSISTENT'
        ))
        ) * 100.0 / (#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll)))

(#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll) FILTER (
        WHERE consistent_dob <> 'CONSISTENT'
        OR consistent_dod = 'AMBIGUOUS'
        OR consistent_race <> 'CONSISTENT'
        OR consistent_sex <> 'CONSISTENT'
        ))
        ) * 100.0 / (#(hll_union_agg(bene_hll)))

__SqlMetric__.verbose_name: % of records where zip code is inconsistent with county code

__TableColumn__.expression:
CASE WHEN 
    dod_earliest is not NULL
    OR dob_latest is not NULL
    OR sex LIKE '%,%'
    OR race LIKE '%,%'
    THEN 'Ambiguous' 
  WHEN  dob is NULL THEN 'Missing DOB'
  ELSE 'Consistent' END
CASE WHEN dob_latest is not NULL THEN 'Ambiguous DOB' end
CASE WHEN dod_earliest is not NULL THEN 'Ambiguous DOD' end
CASE WHEN sex LIKE '%,%' THEN 'Ambiguous Sex'  End
CASE WHEN DOB is NULL THEN 'Missing DOB' end
CASE WHEN race LIKE '%,%' THEN 'Ambiguous Race' End

__TableColumn__.description: Difference between the earliest and latest recorded DOB
__TableColumn__.expression: CASE WHEN dob_latest is NULL THEN NULL ELSE age(dob_latest, dob) END
CASE WHEN dob_latest is NULL THEN NULL ELSE (dob_latest - dob) END

__TableColumn__.description: Differences between dob records in 10 days incrememnts
__TableColumn__.expression:
CASE WHEN dob_latest is NULL THEN NULL ELSE 
        (dob_latest - dob) / 10
    END
